title: Why am I getting responses for a pixel phone when I do not own one?
content: I am just going through all of my basic setup for a new phone after losing my old one I'm trying to update my Google account. When I select help or learn more, I get responses for a pixel phone, which I do not own. I have a LG Rebel 4 LTE. It was purchased in Rifle Colorado at Walmart / Straight Talk Wireless
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device
